      "system_type": "VS",
      "product_type": "fence",
      "name": "VS Vertical Slat Fence",
      "description": "Vertical slat orientation using the same Quickscreen extrusions as QSHS. Vertical slats (XP-6100-S65 / QS-6100-S90) are held by horizontal QS-5000-HORIZ U-channel rails (top and bottom). QS-5800-SF is used as the outer horizontal frame enclosing the U-channel. QS-5800-F is installed vertically at each side of the panel as an edge frame. Same slat SKUs as QSHS — just oriented vertically (cut to height).",
      "active": true,
      "sort_order": 2,
      "metadata": {
        "allowedAngles": [
          90
        ],
